>>And also they tell us
that their fear of death

00:49:43.180 --> 00:49:44.849 align:middle line:84%
is totally gone
after this, that they

00:49:44.849 --> 00:49:48.519 align:middle line:84%
have no more fear
of death whatsoever.

00:49:48.519 --> 00:49:55.092 align:middle line:84%
>>I saw life as an infinite
life, infinite light,

00:49:55.092 --> 00:49:58.429 align:middle line:90%
as an everlasting being.

00:49:58.429 --> 00:50:04.268 align:middle line:84%
We cannot die because we are
already created for to live

