forever.

00:50:05.502 --> 00:50:10.841 align:middle line:84%
The dimension of spirit
is everlasting life.

00:50:10.841 --> 00:50:12.610 align:middle line:84%
>>The third thing
that I have learned

00:50:12.610 --> 00:50:15.246 align:middle line:90%
is that life is forever.

00:50:15.246 --> 00:50:17.348 align:middle line:84%
Death is nothing more
or less than a doorway,

00:50:17.348 --> 00:50:18.983 align:middle line:90%
something you walk through.

00:50:18.983 --> 00:50:20.951 align:middle line:90%
>>Death does not exist.

00:50:20.951 --> 00:50:22.820 align:middle line:90%
Don't be afraid.

00:50:22.820 --> 00:50:27.725 align:middle line:84%
Death is only the part as a
station, railroad station,

00:50:27.725 --> 00:50:31.862 align:middle line:84%
