>>LISA: It is my hope
that this show here

00:50:52.950 --> 00:50:54.885 align:middle line:90%
is a healing for people.

00:50:54.885 --> 00:50:57.955 align:middle line:84%
And your work as well has
been an enormous healing

00:50:57.955 --> 00:51:00.457 align:middle line:84%
for people to not only
explain if they've

00:51:00.457 --> 00:51:03.694 align:middle line:84%
been through this experience,
which I was very lost before.

00:51:03.694 --> 00:51:05.195 align:middle line:84%
I didn't pay attention
to it at all.

00:51:05.195 --> 00:51:08.732 align:middle line:84%
I wanted to deny that that ever
