00:51:11.268 --> 00:51:15.639 align:middle line:84%
And it gave me a doorway into
a sense of belonging, I guess.

00:51:15.639 --> 00:51:17.641 align:middle line:84%
But you have helped
so many people.

00:51:17.641 --> 00:51:21.312 align:middle line:84%
And so what is it that you
