00:51:51.075 --> 00:51:54.645 align:middle line:84%
that what I'm going to be more
remembered for is probably

00:51:54.645 --> 00:52:00.017 align:middle line:84%
my work in conceptualizing
new ways of thinking,

00:52:00.017 --> 00:52:01.986 align:middle line:84%
what you might
broadly call logic.

